## Step 5 — Test naming conventions

| Convention | Example |
|-----------|---------|
| Test file | `{source_file}_test.go` (same directory) |
| Test function | `Test{FunctionName}_{Scenario}` or `Test_{FunctionName}_{Scenario}` |
| Suite struct | `{Feature}TestSuite` or `{Feature}UnitTestSuite` |
| Suite runner | `func Test{Feature}TestSuite(t *testing.T) { suite.Run(t, new(...)) }` |
| Table case name | Short, descriptive: `"ready pool"`, `"empty input"`, `"db error"` |
| Subtest | `t.Run(tc.name, func(t *testing.T) { ... })` |

